FUNCTION: FUNCTION: Plays a role in signal transduction by regulating the intracellular concentration of cyclic nucleotides. This phosphodiesterase catalyzes the specific hydrolysis of cGMP to 5'-GMP (PubMed:8530505). Specifically regulates nitric-oxide-generated cGMP (By similarity). {ECO:0000250|UniProtKB:O76074, ECO:0000269|PubMed:8530505}.
